text: Ishani Shrestha () (born May 5, 1991) in Kathmandu, Nepal is a Nepali model, media personality, entrepreneur and the title holder of Miss Nepal 2013. She represented Nepal in Miss World beauty pageant 2013 and won the title of Beauty with a Purpose by securing a top ten position. ==References== Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Nepalese beauty pageant winners Category:Miss Nepal winners Category:Nepalese models Category:People from Kathmandu
